---
title: One-Pan Turkey Stir-Fry Tacos with Tangy Slaw, Sriracha Mayo & Wonton Strips
description: We’re always up for a sweet and savory dinner pairing, and these genre-defying tacos are just that. Chicken breast strips are cooked in a sweet soy glaze until the glaze is sticky and the chicken is tender. They’re stuffed into steamy tortillas, along with a tangy, cilantro-flecked cabbage slaw. Of course, we’d never skip out on taco toppings, and these ones don’t disappoint: There’s creamy, spicy sriracha mayo and crispy wonton strips. It’s all ready in just 15 minutes—life is sweet (and savory), friends.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6679ab4f718be5f7bc559778-c526226a.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/667c392ae4ccb870eb4dc615-en-US.pdf
cuisine: Asian
